text: Colobothea bicuspidata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pierre André Latreille in 1811. It is known from Bolivia, Brazil, Colombia, Peru, Ecuador, and French Guiana."Colobothea bicuspidata". BioLib.
